column29: Costs of sales includes costs for computer games development.
column31: Other external costs comprise costs for sales, administration, premises, loss on debtors.
column32: Other operating income includes grants for the company's development activities.
column38: The board of directors and the managing director have today presented the annual report of Tactile Games ApS for the financial year 1 January to 31 December 2018.
column41: We are of the opinion that the management's review includes a fair description of the issues dealt with.
column52: The annual report is recommended for approval by the general meeting.
